description:
A free app for the electric music side jedentageinset.de
"Quality instead of Quantity"

A german site for electronic music with a set every day.

Our set collection already fills multiple hard disks and the orange cloud is basically our home. Regularly
we search through it for new treasures. On weekends we show up in clubs all around Germany, always on the search for the perfect set.

The Jedentageinset app can be used as a companion for NewPipe or SoundCloud.
